import React, { Fragment } from 'react';
import styled from 'styled-components';
import { Link } from 'react-router-dom';

const MacNavContainer = styled.div`
    background-color: rgb(246, 246, 246);
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    align-items: center;
`;

const MacNav = styled.div`
	width: 860px;
	display: flex;
	flex-direction: row;
	justify-content: space-between;
`;

const IconDiv = styled.div`
	padding-bottom: 3rem;
	display: flex;
	flex-direction: column;
	justify-content: center;
	align-items: center;
	font-size: 1.1rem;
`;

const MacImg = styled.img`
	width: 65px;
`;

const MacPro = styled.img`
    width: 33px;
`

const LittleMac = styled.img`
    width: 40px;
`

const Accessories = styled.img`
    width: 40px;
`

export default function Mac() {
	return (
		<Fragment>
			<MacNavContainer>
				<MacNav>
					<IconDiv>
						<Link to="/mac/macbook">
							<MacImg src="macbook.png" alt="macbook" />
						</Link>
						Macbook
					</IconDiv>
					<IconDiv>
						<Link to="/mac/macbook-air">
							<MacImg src="macbook-air.png" alt="macbook" />
						</Link>
						Macbook Air
					</IconDiv>
					<IconDiv>
						<Link to="/mac/macbook-pro">
							<MacImg src="macbook-pro.png" alt="macbook" />
						</Link>
						Macbook Pro
					</IconDiv>
					<IconDiv>
						<Link to="/mac/macbook">
							<MacImg src="imac.png" alt="macbook" />
						</Link>
						iMac
					</IconDiv>
					<IconDiv>
						<Link to="/mac/macbook">
							<MacImg src="imac-pro.png" alt="macbook" />
						</Link>
						iMac Pro
					</IconDiv>
					<IconDiv>
						<Link to="/mac/macbook">
							<MacPro src="mac-pro.png" alt="macbook" />
						</Link>
						Mac Pro
					</IconDiv>
					<IconDiv>
						<Link to="/mac/macbook">
							<LittleMac src="mac-mini.png" alt="macbook" />
						</Link>
						Mac mini
					</IconDiv>
					<IconDiv>
						<Link to="/mac/macbook">
							<Accessories src="accessories.png" alt="macbook" />
						</Link>
						Macbook
					</IconDiv>
					<IconDiv>
						<Link to="/mac/macbook">
							<MacImg src="mojave.png" alt="macbook" />
						</Link>
						Macbook
					</IconDiv>
					<IconDiv>
						<Link to="/mac/macbook">
							<MacImg src="compare.png" alt="macbook" />
						</Link>
						Macbook
					</IconDiv>
				</MacNav>
			</MacNavContainer>
			hey you're in /mac!
		</Fragment>
	);
}
